Programs.LongDescription: Four zoo animals accidentally find themselves enroute to Africa, learning first-hand what life in the wild can be like in this animated family comedy. 在纽约的中央公园里，狮子、斑马、长颈鹿和河马是一群热爱表演的好朋友。某天晚上，一位成员的失踪，让其他人决定挣脱铁笼前往搜寻。拯救工作一开始非常顺利，后来却让牠们落脚非洲，体验真正的野性生活。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 马达加斯加 Madagascar

Programs.LongDescription: With unravelled embroidery and fraying hems, the Pants are back for another glorious summer that the four friends will never forget. 莉娜的夏天沈浸在绘画与恋爱之中，担心自己会忘记柯斯塔；卡门则受到大学同学的煽动，以为争取角色是人生最重要的事...
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 牛仔裤的夏天2 The Sisterhood Of The Traveling Pants 2

Programs.LongDescription: Vin Diesel and Paul Walker lead a reunion of returning all-stars in the biggest thrill ride of this explosive franchise built on speed. 退休警察布莱恩和金盆洗手的歹徒唐，，加上同系列电影所有要角，黑白两道连手完成一项超速任务
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 玩命关头5 Fast Five

Programs.LongDescription: To lower the crime rate, the New Founding Fathers of America test a sociological theory that vents aggression for one night in one isolated community. 美国新开国元勋为了将犯罪率降到1%以下，在某个被隔离的地区进行社会学理论的测试，即实验性实施一夜杀戮的制度。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 杀戮元年 The First Purge

Programs.LongDescription: A top-secret project on genetically-enhanced sharks goes awry when these highly intelligent super-sharks turn on their masters and begin to pick them off one by one. 对鲨鱼进行基因强化的实验出现差错，这些高智力的超级鲨鱼开始攻击创造出牠们的科学家，引发致命的结果。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 水深火热2 Deep Blue Sea 2

Programs.LongDescription: A couple who decides to start a family and adopt through the foster-care system, find themselves raising three wild kids who have no interest in being parented. 一对夫妻打算成立一个真正的家庭，于是透过领养制度收养了三个完全不受控的孩子……
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 速成家庭 Instant Family

Programs.LongDescription: As a young couple goes from college romance to marriage and the birth of their first child, there are unexpected twists in their journey. 一对从大学时期就开始交往的年轻情侣，迈向婚姻后迎来他们的第一个孩子，美好的人生却出现意外的转折。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 生命中的美好意外 Life Itself

Programs.LongDescription: Reagan Willis has one dream, to play soccer like her hero Alex Morgan. When Reagan accidentally hitting her head, her poster of Alex Morgan suddenly comes to life. 蕾根威利斯的梦想是成为和偶像亚历克丝摩根一样厉害的足球高手。在蕾根意外撞到头时，她海报上的亚历克丝竟变成真人……
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 亚历克丝和我 Alex & Me

Programs.LongDescription: A true story of a girl who pretends to be a boy who identifies as a transgender and how she dupes the elite, the rich and the famous. 这个深具吸引力的真实故事深入JT勒罗伊骗局背后的一切。一名女子假装双性恋男子，愚弄了好莱坞的富人与名人，时尚界与文学菁英圈。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 神秘作家:勒罗伊 Jt Leroy

Programs.LongDescription: Two bickering single parents are stuck with each other when their families are forced to share a suite for a week at a resort. 两个互相看不顺眼的单亲爸妈各自带孩子度假，却碰在一起，而且整个星期都得共享渡假村的套房.....
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 当我们混在一起 Blended

Programs.LongDescription: Facing competition from a new generation of racers, Lightning McQueen attempts to shine once again in the sport that he loves with the help of a young race technician. 闪电麦昆面对新世代赛车的竞争，靠着年轻的赛车技师的协助，企图再次在场上发光发热。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: Cars 3:闪电再起 Cars 3

Programs.LongDescription: Vin Diesel and Paul Walker lead a reunion of returning all-stars in the biggest thrill ride of this explosive franchise built on speed. 退休警察布莱恩和金盆洗手的歹徒唐，，加上同系列电影所有要角，黑白两道连手完成一项超速任务
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 玩命关头5 Fast Five

Programs.LongDescription: Steven Spielberg's masterpiece follows a team of scientists on an island to witness real dinosaurs in a park, only to see everything go wrong when a storm hits. 大企业家成功在小岛上复育各式恐龙,他找来几位恐龙专家,要让世人大开眼界,史帝芬史匹伯当年以此片掀起了全球恐龙潮.观众千万别错过这部精彩的经典电影!
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 侏罗纪公园 Jurassic Park

Programs.LongDescription: As global warming melts their icy environments, the Ice Age sub-zero heroes survive a flood and emerge as a unified family. 气候变暖融化了冰原英雄们的生活环境，大伙努力在洪水中求生存，变成密不可分的家人。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 冰原历险记2 Ice Age: The Meltdown

Programs.LongDescription: Angelina Jolie stars as treasure hunter, Lara Croft, hunting down the Triangle of Light. 安洁莉娜裘莉、强沃特主演,本片呈现出一位有血有肉的致命女杰，裘莉在片中骑大车、玩大枪、展露惹火的身材，「古墓奇兵」可是来势汹汹非同小可。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 古墓奇兵 Lara Croft: Tomb Raider

Programs.LongDescription: Angelina Jolie returns as a psyched and pumped up adventurer out to battle evil. 安洁莉娜裘莉饰演的冒险家又回来了！她已准备好且很兴奋要再次对抗邪恶势力！
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 古墓奇兵2：风起云涌 Lara Croft Tomb Raider: The Cradle Of Life

Programs.LongDescription: A half-human, half-Atlantean man goes on a journey to see if he has what it takes to be the rightful king of Atlantis. 拥有一半亚特兰提斯血统的人类阿瑟库瑞展开旅程，确认自己是否足以担当与生俱来的天命…成为一名国王。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 水行侠 Aquaman

Programs.LongDescription: A hitman who spent his entire life killing must now save a life when a young woman seeks refuge in his cabin after a near death accident. 一个一辈子都在杀戮的杀手在一名差点死于非命的年轻女子来到他的小屋寻求庇护后，做了一个令人难以想象的决定…去拯救一条生命。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 冷血遗产 Cold Blood Legacy

Programs.LongDescription: A young man is falsely imprisoned but manages to escape and sets about exacting revenge on those responsible for his imprisonment. 本片改编自同名小说，剧情描述被诬陷入狱的年轻男子打算逃狱，对那些害他入狱的人展开报复。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 绝世英豪 The Count Of Monte Cristo

Programs.LongDescription: The Addams family welcomes a new addition and hires a nanny who captures the heart of Uncle Fester. 你最不想与之为邻的阿达一家人又回来了！本片由执导过「MIB星际战警」、「飙风战警」等片的导演巴瑞索纳费德，为这部改编自经典电视影集的黑色喜剧掌镜。

Programs.LongDescription: A spectacular retelling of The Iliad, Troy is an epic tale of passion, heroism, betrayal and war. 金球奖得主布莱德彼特、艾瑞克巴纳与奥兰多布鲁，在特洛伊战争中勇敢追求不朽的名声，期望世人永远称颂其光荣事迹。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 特洛伊：木马屠城 Troy

Programs.LongDescription: In the sleepy small town of Centerville, the dead rise from their graves and savagely attack and feast on the living – and the citizens must battle for their survival. 在寂静的森特威尔小镇，丧尸从坟墓中爬出，残暴攻击与追捕人类，为了求生，居民们拼命奋战。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 丧尸未逝 The Dead Don't Die

Programs.LongDescription: A California-based writer from Afghanistan must return home to face his past after a phone call from a friend of his father's. 在一次放风筝比赛中，哈山前去寻回阿米尔的风筝，却遭到恶少攻击，而阿米尔竟只是袖手旁观。多年后，成为畅销作家的阿米尔在加州安顿下来，却收到一通来自远方的电话，使他不得不重新回到过往，面对那段黑暗的往事。
Programs.TvProgramTitle: 追风筝的孩子 The Kite Runner

Programs.LongDescription: Chris Evans stars as Captain America, who leads the fight for freedom as the ultimate weapon against evil. 当邪恶势力扬言威胁全球，美国队长将率领队伍捍卫自由，对抗以红骷髅为首的纳粹党神秘科学组织九头蛇军团宣战，一场正邪大战就此展开。

Programs.LongDescription: In a distant and beautiful forest town, the animals live in harmony.
